{"tid":113836,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片)The ONE贈甘比 李嘉欣咁樣樣","createTime":"2017-02-09T09:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T12:06:15.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a457d3145b1333d3e8de1b54a272190c3e72d685","tid":113836,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"一個美麗的誤會，誤會了近11年。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴The ONE究竟係咪大劉劉鑾雄當年為李嘉欣而命名？唔係。身家超過千二億嘅大劉，早前將私人名下、市值約180億港元嘅The ONE送咗俾甘比，令甘比身家升至逾300億，成為香港女首富。而大劉接受《蘋果》獨家訪問時，亦澄清「The ONE」呢個名，係劉鳴煒全權負責改嘅，大劉根本由頭到尾冇參與過&hellip;&hellip;(新聞連結: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2k63Ieq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2k63Ieq&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8QIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=76311e9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2k63Ieq</a> )<br />\n<br />\n今日大美人李嘉欣到樂富出席活動，笑晒現身，美艷如昔，大談滑雪之旅、拉頭馬同埋忘記老公亨亨嘅生日。訪問到尾聲時，記者問嘉欣可知大劉送咗The ONE俾甘比？嘉欣呆咗一秒，「er&hellip;&hellip;冇留意呀真係，講真。好忙呀！點樣呢？」笑笑口撥頭髮。<br />\n<br />\n提到甘比已為香港女首富，嘉欣即說，笑笑口咁說:「咁係好呀！咁係一件好事。」加一句：「心中富有係最緊要。哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n多年來外間一直將大劉嘅The ONE同李嘉欣拉上關係，估唔到依家先至知原來冇關係，李嘉欣聞言保持微笑:「我冇呀&hellip;你依家講我先至有聽呢個事，係囉，忙碌喺自己嘅事，所以都冇乜時間留意其他人嘅新聞。」訪問完畢，嘉欣仲禮貌地說Thank You。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170209&amp;guid=56281967&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170209%26guid%3D56281967%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8QIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=2789acfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170209%26guid%3D56281967%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=6f0bfe42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170209&amp;guid=56281967&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"35d317fc93c48232489667daa74119ea4f00574e","tid":113836,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"我真係"},{"pid":"52104d07b0b8287b95def4cfca84d8a0fdb61ee3","tid":113836,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係</blockquote><br />\n恭喜佢呀！"},{"pid":"9b0c35fe8caebdcecf04af70e4aee3ec380e5e90","tid":113836,"uid":44007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:11:06.000Z","msg":"對甘比仲好"},{"pid":"17eeee305d3657214d837390b7fb1ece8fe8ae9e","tid":113836,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"180億既禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfa3f0263e0a87d0f586e18219910a9d182ca34","tid":113836,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"我得180億精蟲做禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220e6469ed2e092e571c935be0f2e8ea8402719e","tid":113836,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"而家李嘉欣一舉一動都係笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}